{"word":"σκιάω","slug":"σκιάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σκιάω</b></el> <el>(σκιάω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:σκιάζω'><el>σκιάζω</el></a>\n<p/><i>to overshadow</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be shaded</i> or <i>become dark</i>, <el>σκιόωντο ἀγυιαί</el> (epic 3rd <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>) <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/>"}]}